{"name":"Second Life","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"This guild member leads a second life with a particularly convincing ‘cover identity’. Perhaps she is a noble, a merchant, or a ship owner. The second life provides both access to locations that might otherwise be out-of- bounds and to information. The second life provides no additional income – i.e. a merchant business only breaks even, providing information and access, but not income.<p>You can draw upon the influence of your second life once per game session, this requires a Smarts roll. Failure indicates that you weren’t able to obtain what you needed, while a success provides you with useful information or temporary access to a specialized device or location. On a raise, you gain access to highly detailed information or superior resources.<p>The precise nature of the second life must be chosen when this Edge is taken, and it determines what sort of information and resources are available.","notes":"Guild of Shadows page 10","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"N, Sm d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.guild-of-shadows.UgejpDToQ5jnErcI"},"cf":{"id":"temp_8m8awrrszmi","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Guild of Shadows","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"3kLLpgcynWFHmnrL"}
{"name":"Wraith","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The wraith is a highly trained assassin able to catch his opponent off-guard and strike in an instant. He may spend a benny to automatically get the drop on an opponent.","notes":"Agents of Oblivion page 35","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"L, Ghost, Stealth d8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tjb1fblf39r","path":"Core Edges#/CF_SEP/Agents of Oblivion","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.agents-of-oblivion-edges.yBrDcdduIIljEwFT"}},"_id":"3q1zDBEVDrRZRTOl"}
{"name":"Glide It In","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"While in an airborne vehicle the hero may spend a benny when called upon to roll on the Out of Control, Altitude Change, or vehicle Critical Hits tables. On the former, the benny reduces the result by one category, whereas for the latter two tables it allows the character to shift the category up or down one category, as desired. The benny is spent after the appropriate roll is made on the respective table.","notes":"Expanded Profession - The Ace page 2","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Ace, Sky Maneuver, Agility d8+, Piloting d10+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.expanded-profession-investigator.3MEeTI3im5u6Y8Dl"},"cf":{"id":"temp_sebdvv9ult","path":"Core Edges#/CF_SEP/Expanded Profession - The Ace","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"3q6EmgipzvyMc3j8"}
{"name":"Hacker","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"As a hacker, you are committed to learning everything you can about the science (or art) of cracking into secure systems. Your skills give you an edge in many situations, whether you are using your TAP to shut down an opponent’s Cybertech, or when you use a hacking rig to invade corporate mainframes.</p><p>You gain the use of programs and begin play with two programs of your choice. You must meet the requirements to use the program, however. Hacking is the skill you use to launch your programs. You may obtain more programs by choosing the “New Power” Edge. Finally, If using the Bring the Pain plugin (page 120), you get +1 Toughness to resist Intrusion Countermeasures.","notes":"Interface Zero 3.0 Players Guide page 44","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6, Hacking d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.interface-zero-30.8072qF9MkIoWlvxL"},"cf":{"id":"temp_zys386iohka","path":"Science Fiction Edges#/CF_SEP/Interface Zero 3.0","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"42UuNT2PNf0GCgSu"}
