{"name":"Artificer","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"All items created require the crafter to create or obtain a schema of the arcane device’s design. Consumable items such as potions or herbal remedies require the arcane skill roll upon creation rather than at the time of use. The creator knows immediately whether her arcane skill roll succeeded or failed.","notes":"Eberron Conversion page 32","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"As presented in the Savage Worlds core rules, but with the following modifications."}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.eberron.FPC1syKtGUzpAeeJ"},"cf":{"id":"temp_hgfoxjk4syj","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Eberron","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"4V72inEKKfiSqnpj"}
{"name":"Noble","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Noble is the equivalent of coming from a wealthy or notable family concerned about their public appearance. The kid gets the usual benefits listed in Savage Worlds (+2 Charisma and the Rich Edge), but is pressured to stay out of trouble and “keep his nose clean.” How this affects the student is up to the Dean, but visits from “Daddy” and local media attention should be expected.","notes":"East Texas University page 16","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Freshman"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.east-texas-university.3qASHBf1My93ZfrK"},"cf":{"id":"temp_j3gsmia1ap","path":"Horror Edges#/CF_SEP/East Texas University","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"4VRDhzVSQRaKwxNZ"}
{"name":"Iron Jaw","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The hero can take and shrug off even the most extreme blows. He gets +2 to Soak rolls and Vigor rolls to avoid Knock-Out Blows (see page 74).","notes":"Flash Gordon page 40","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Vigor d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.flash-gordon.HNXJSMydbg6PbADC"},"cf":{"id":"temp_zc5n98io8as","path":"Science Fiction Edges#/CF_SEP/Flash Gordon","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"4gsdoT5ANbsuCuh3"}
