{"name":"Action Surge","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The adventurer can spend a Prophecy Shard to take one additional action on her turn. This action does not add or include a Multi-Action penalty. Any other actions on that turn are still accounted for when determining the penalty for those other actions.","notes":"Eberron Conversion page 31","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Wild Card, Seasoned"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.eberron.f3bmtghAfz1ixhJN"},"cf":{"id":"temp_hgfoxjk4syj","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Eberron","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"hypua6nBDrFfm8mD"}
{"name":"Hacker","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The agent is a master of penetrating electronic and computer security systems. He receives +2 to all Tech Ops rolls and any Investigation rolls where he has access to a computer. Each attempt to penetrate a system’s defenses takes 10 minutes instead of the normal hour.","notes":"Agents of Oblivion page 29","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"N, Sm d8, Tech Ops d10"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tjb1fblf39r","path":"Core Edges#/CF_SEP/Agents of Oblivion","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.agents-of-oblivion-edges.DbG2pMz5slZb9omt"}},"_id":"i1lCGCXlJC3chwLS"}
{"name":"Calm Before the Storm","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Whether from meditation, taking time to gather energies, or careful repeating the magic words he will have to pronounce, the hero spends time preparing before unleashing fury on his enemies.</p><p> When the hero takes his entire turn focusing his magic (no movement, no Multi-Actions, can’t be Shaken or Stunned), he gets to ignore up to 2 points of penalties (including Multi-Action penalties) on each power he activates on his next turn. If not used on that next turn, the focus is lost.","notes":"Fantasy: Wizards and Mystics page 44","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (any)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.fantasy-add-ons.0DN9Jbx68nNktVJj"},"cf":{"id":"temp_bseilocyflu","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Fantasy Add-Ons","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"iF7oR6wavPTzW2QS"}
