{"name":"Road Maneuver","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Select one maneuver with a penalty that is allowed by a ground craft. When performing this ground craft maneuver you have a +2 to your roll but only to cancel out part of or the entire penalty. This bonus cannot increase your roll beyond your normal, unmodified ability.</p><p>You cannot apply this Edge to the so-called unnamed maneuver unless an entirely new one is outright designed and named.","notes":"Expanded Profession - The Ace page 3","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Agility d8+, Ace, Driving d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.expanded-profession-ace.2UMeZkUfMrfTw2tN"},"cf":{"id":"temp_4q51ympbhi4","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Expanded Profession - Ace","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"ki4q1hEv7ueEA5dg"}
