{"name":"Monster Hunter International","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"MHI team members are known for their dedication and gung-ho nature. Any MHI team members can share Bennies with other MHI teammates they can see.","notes":"Monster Hunters International page 135","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Acceptance into MHI"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.monster-hunter-international.AaEwhKp0C06bGzsa"},"cf":{"id":"temp_mt92hgg82to","path":"Horror Edges#/CF_SEP/Monster Hunter International","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"nJ1Ke8xDkPHxtv8v"}
{"name":"Born On The Streets","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"This character was raised in a poor neighborhood and learned at a young age how to survive in such a harsh environment. Like many others, she had to commit crimes and outsmart the cops. She may ignore up to 2 points of penalties due to security when committing crimes.","notes":"Wiseguys page 52","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.wiseguys.XtFVcPO2kpW9m3ji"},"cf":{"id":"temp_o9gz86yz6om","path":"Core Edges#/CF_SEP/Wiseguys","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"nQT01m865oWXalCe"}
{"name":"Berserk Luck","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"When going Berserk, the adventurer has a greater ability to alter her luck than most others do. This Edge grants 1 temporary Prophecy Shard while going Berserk. If the adventurer doesn’t use this Prophecy Shard while going Berserk, it disappears when it ends.","notes":"Eberron Conversion page 28","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Wild Card, Novice, Berserk"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.eberron.rknelOfL4aELf2Ag"},"cf":{"id":"temp_hgfoxjk4syj","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Eberron","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"nilq5QE9kK1yrvcd"}
{"name":"Strike Team Kiratowa","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"As long as you can see another member of the STK, you can add a monsters size to your damage roll. You also gain +2 on Skill tests involving advanced or experimental science.","notes":"Monster Hunters International page 136","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Acceptance into the STK, Seasoned."}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.monster-hunter-international.pJpT1VFm0jQyjEHg"},"cf":{"id":"temp_mt92hgg82to","path":"Horror Edges#/CF_SEP/Monster Hunter International","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"noZQRxinMteBFayK"}
{"_id":"nuZI1UbYCZtiFDra","name":"Courage Under Fire","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"This leader might just have a guardian angel. Bullets and even artillery fragments seem to whiz right by him, especially when he’s doing his duty and commanding those placed under his command.</p><p>If your character is standing and not in cover, roll a die for every successful attack that would wound him (including Area Effect attacks). If the die roll is odd, the hero takes no damage. Otherwise he’s affected normally.","notes":"Weird War I","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"26"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"RX3k8ETYyqlbZDTC":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.weird-war-i-edges.iXAp5UyMssy57eEt"},"cf":{"id":"temp_6j8uzj9fx9s","path":"Weird War I","color":"#000000"}}}
