{"name":"Spell Punch","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"When you draw a Joker, double the damage of your first successful Wandslinging attack this round. This may be <i>blast, bolt, burst, </i>or any other power that deals direct damage.","notes":"Wand Magic page 5","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"WC, N, AB (Wand Magic), Wandslinging d8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.wand-magic.M4roBpNP5FZGF1SP"},"cf":{"id":"temp_cul0097oeo7","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Wand Magic","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"z3ERkiZUSNTj8cKJ"}
{"name":"Transporter Chief","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"What piece of technology is more subtle and more versatile than the transporter? Performing complex tasks with the transporter is normally penalized, e.g...</p><p>• Boarding an enemy ship during combat: –2</p><p>• Beaming \"site-to-site\": –2</p><p>• Storing someone long-term in the computer: –4</p><p>• Beaming the knife out of an enemy's hand: –4</p><p>• Duplicating a person: –6</p><p>• Opening a door to the Mirror Universe: –6</p><p>With this edge, you are a proven transporter expert. You ignore up to 4 penalties when performing complex transporter actions.","notes":"Star Trek page 8","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran; Knowledge (Starship Operations) d10; Knowledge (Astronomy) d6; Knowledge (Computers) d6."}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.star-trek.3aeb2K9r7xAfAs4P"},"cf":{"id":"temp_bgph7dksida","path":"Science Fiction Edges#/CF_SEP/Star Trek","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"z3x4H4QhfjaFyy5a"}
{"name":"Piloting Test","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Maintaining this increased speed is risky, however, applying a cumulative -2 penalty to all Driving, Piloting, or Boating Tests per consecutive round the abnormal speed is sustained.","notes":"Expanded Profession - The Ace page 3","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.expanded-profession-ace.00atej5bwqLTGsOm"},"cf":{"id":"temp_4q51ympbhi4","path":"Fantasy Edges#/CF_SEP/Expanded Profession - Ace","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"zDbpJ2YbroZtupq7"}
